B.N0=new A.hn("CV Website",B.dx,"I developed and designed my personal CV website using Flutter, showcasing my skills, experience, and accomplishments in a dynamic and visually appealing way. The website features a responsive layout, ensuring optimal performance across various devices, and includes interactive elements for an engaging user experience. By utilizing Flutter's powerful capabilities, I was able to create a seamless and modern web application that highlights my expertise in both front-end design and back-end integration","https://vmakris.info",B.hQ)
B.N1=new A.hn("Basic Task App (Full-Stack)",B.dx,"I developed a full-stack task management application using Flutter for the front-end, with a focus on creating an intuitive and user-friendly interface. This project marked my first experience with backend development, where I learned and implemented basic Node.js, TypeScript, Docker, PostgreSQL, nodemon, drizzleORM and dotenv for the back-end. The app features secure user authentication, task creation, and management, with real-time updates. By combining these technologies, I gained valuable hands-on experience in both front-end and back-end development, further enhancing my skill set in building complete, scalable applications.","",B.hQ)
B.N2=new A.hn("Basic Blog/Notes App (Full-Stack)",B.dx,"I developed a full-stack blog and notes posting application utilizing Supabase as a Backend-as-a-Service (BaaS). The application incorporates Supabase features such as Authentication, Storage, and Database. Users can create an account using their email, sign in securely, and perform CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations on their personal blog posts. The front-end of the application is built with Flutter, providing a seamless and responsive user experience.","",B.hQ)
